		"description": "Update cmake to 3.14.0-rc1. The latest GA 3.13.4 has a bug with WinRT project references which broke app builds. This update is to enable use to further modernize our project definitions in the future, as well as hopefully improve performance (which we may need to do further tweaks to our build process to have cmake drive msbuild as cwilliams did here: https://github.com/appcelerator/HAL/pull/90/commits/e8741b3b62ab81e0ff0135f06ce51638782b046b#diff-58231b16fdee45a03a4ee3cf94a9f2c3R19\r\n\r\nThis also relates to https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile_windows/pull/1346. We noticed the previous attempt to update CMake configuration made the app performance 5x times slower than before. We might want to see why.\r\n\r\n",
